name: Lt. Governor Billy Nungesser
tweet: A Harvey, Louisiana native, Zaila Avant-garde, just won the Scripps National Spelling Bee! Can’t wait to welcome home Zaila. She's a real Louisiana Ambassador! Your state is so proud of you! #LouisianaStrong  https://t.co/y1iPM0Phl4

name: Lt. Governor Billy Nungesser
tweet: UPDATE: Live music, Fairs and Festivals are BACK. With certain safety guidelines, we are able—once again—to attend the events we love so much and support the musicians who make us who we are. A great day for Louisiana. #LouisianaStrong #COVIDupdate #OnlyLouisiana

name: Lt. Governor Billy Nungesser
tweet: A sincere congratulations to Louisiana's own, @DeVontaSmith_6, on becoming only the third Louisiana-born winner of the Heisman Trophy.  Congratulations, Devonta, on making history and making us all so proud. #LouisianaStrong
